text: Volkmar Kuttelwascher (born 8 October 1969) is an Austrian rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Austria Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Linz
